text: Contoderopsis luzonica is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Breuning in 1970.Biolib.cz - Contoderopsis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Acanthocinini Category:Beetles described in 1970 Category:Taxa named by Stephan von Breuning
